However, on [August 10, 2021](rescind_date), [Owen Talbot](rescinder) rescinded [the contract](contract_name) as [Owen Talbot](minor) was a minor at the time of the transaction. Katz](potential_buyer) for a higher price.

This rescission was made due to [Bob's](threatener) threat to [Chuck](victim) on [20/August/1998](duress_date), as he wanted to sell [this_flat](purchase_product) to [Faythe](potential_buyer) for a higher price.

However, on [17 February, 2012](rescind_date), [Zoe Campbell](rescinder) rescinded [the agreement](contract_name) as [Zoe Campbell](minor) was a minor at the time of the transaction. This rescission was made due to [Max Stanley's](threatener) threat to [Zoe Campbell](victim) on [21 February, 2012](duress_date), as he wanted to sell [the building](purchase_product) to [Angela S. Hampton](potential_buyer) for a higher price.

However, this rescission was made because [Owen Holt](threatener) threatened [Joshua Gallagher](victim) on [January 27, 2023](duress_date). It is because [Owen Holt](seller) would like to sell [the apartment](purchase_product) to [Naomi Manning](potential_buyer) in the higher price.
